        "creation_date": 1520589842,
        "body": "<p>i think you're mistaken on what @Data does. @Data combines a bunch of other annotations into one. it doesn't generate code for you. it performs annotations on code you have written. <\/p>\n\n<p>I highly recommend reading <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/41979374/does-the-project-lombok-data-annotation-create-a-constructor-of-any-kind\">Does the project lombok data annotation create a constructor of any kind<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>This link actually references the appropriate <a href=\"https://projectlombok.org/features/Data\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">lombok data page<\/a> itself.<\/p>\n",
